explanation: [0-0] In a room with beige tile flooring, a woman wearing a pink short-sleeved top and blue jeans is cleaning the wall with a long-handled brush with black and white bristles.

[0-10] As the woman drags the brush, another image of "herself" appears on the wall. This image gradually emerges, starting from the head and revealing the whole body. The upper body of the image is the woman, and the lower body is an animal. Then the image enlarges, and the woman hits the lower body away with the brush. She then drags the brush on the wall again, and the image of her lower body appears. She drags the lower body to the upper body, forming a complete "her." Now, there are two identical women in the room, standing face to face. They greet each other, and then the woman on the right hits the woman on the left out of the frame.
